Today, Hon'ble Minister of Civil Aviation, Sh. Kinjarapu Rammohan Naidu @RamMNK, in the presence of Hon'ble Tamilnadu State Industries Minister, Sh. T.R.B. Rajaa @TRBRajaa , Chairman, AAI, Sh. Vipin Kumar @vipinkumarIAS, Joint Secretary, MoCA, Ms. Rubina Ali and senior officials from the Ministry of Civil Aviation and the Airports Authority of India inaugurated the UDAN Yatri Café  operated by Travel Food Services at Chennai International Airport.  

This newly introduced facility offers budget-friendly snacks and refreshments for travellers on the move. Strategically located at the Pre-Check-in Area of T-1, the café provides an easily accessible refreshment option for departing passengers, adding to the range of amenities aimed at enhancing passenger convenience. Empowering abilities—Udan Yatri Cafe is managed by Specially Abled Staff who serve with passion. |

